        "action": "Remove Vehicle Excise Duty and add the cost to Fuel Duty",
        "additional_details": "To encourage people to drive less polluting vehicles and also making the people that use the roads most pay more for their upkeep.",
        "background": "Abolish Vehicle Excise Duty and add the cost to a litre of fuel, so the more economical the vehicle you drive - the less you pay. This should encourage people to drive more responsibly and also benefit the environment.",
